        <title>Docker镜像存储路径与containerd踩坑总结</title>
        <link>https://ynhugo.github.io/p/docker%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8Econtainerd%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</link>
